   <concept id="i1099698"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.2"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">19.1309</ph> 
          Contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1266e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
               </p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1266e15" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        The contracting officer shall insert the clause <xref href="FAR-i1057314.dita#i1057314"
                              base="i1057314"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.219-3</xref>, Notice of HUBZone Set-Aside or Sole Source Award, in solicitations and contracts for acquisitions that are set aside or awarded on a sole source basis to, HUBZone small business concerns under <xref href="FAR-i1099604.dita#i1099604"
                              base="i1099604"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.1305</xref> or <xref href="FAR-i1099639.dita#i1099639"
                              base="i1099639"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.1306</xref>. This includes multiple-award contracts when orders may be set aside for HUBZone small business concerns as described in <xref href="FAR-i1117805.dita#i1117805"
                              base="i1117805"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">8.405-5</xref> and <xref href="FAR-i1104008.dita#i1104008"
                              base="i1104008"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">16.505</xref>(b)(2)(i)(F) or when orders may be issued directly to one HUBZone small business concern in accordance with <xref href="FAR-19.504.dita#id203CEK0I0HS"
                              base="id203CEK0I0HS"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.504</xref>(c)(1)(ii).</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1266e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        The contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate I to waive the 50 percent requirement if the conditions at <xref href="FAR-i1099682.dita#i1099682"
                              base="i1099682"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.1308</xref>(c) apply.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1266e47" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
               </p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1266e52" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1057352.dita#i1057352"
                              base="i1057352"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.219-4</xref>, Notice of Price Evaluation Preference for HUBZone Small Business Concerns, in solicitations and contracts for acquisitions conducted using full and open competition.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1266e60" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        The contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate I to waive the 50 percent requirement if the conditions at <xref href="FAR-i1099682.dita#i1099682"
                              base="i1099682"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.1308</xref>(c) apply.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1266e68" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  For use of clause <xref href="FAR-i52_219-33.dita#id203KG0I04WS"
                        base="id203KG0I04WS"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-33</xref>, Nonmanufacturer Rule, see the prescription at <xref href="FAR-i1100931.dita#i1100931"
                        base="i1100931"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(h)(2).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
